      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Petra is like a jigsaw fragmented &amp; pieces missing" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Petra is like a jigsaw fragmented &amp; pieces missing" href="/user/show/1237196-petra-is-like-a-jigsaw-fragmented-pieces-missing">Petra is like a jigsaw fragmented &amp; pieces missing</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>


          <div><span class="uitext greyText">Recommends it for: </span>
           <span class="uitext reviewText">Everyone in the entire world</span></div>

        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/1237196-petra-is-like-a-jigsaw-fragmented-pieces-missing?shelf=reviewed">reviewed</a>, 
